Chalkboard art is ephemeral.<ref name=stub/>

==Chalkboard artists==
Chalkboard artists include [[Catherine Owens]], [[Chris Yoon]], [[Maggie Choate]], [[Bryce Wisdom]].<ref name=stub/>

